@startuml
title Calculator System — Module Component Boundaries (PR #444)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "__main__\n(entry point)" as Main
component "cli" as CLI
component "interactive" as Interactive
component "operation_registry" as Registry
component "calculator" as Calc
component "history" as History

database "history.txt\n(filesystem)" as HistFile

note top of Main
  if len(sys.argv) > 1:
    run_cli(); sys.exit(rc)
  else:
    run_interactive_session()
end note

Main --> CLI : if CLI args present\n(run_cli)
Main --> Interactive : if no args\n(run_interactive_session)

CLI --> Registry : instantiates per invocation
CLI --> Calc : instantiates per invocation

Interactive --> Registry : instantiates once per session
Interactive --> Calc : instantiates once per session
Interactive --> History : instantiates once per session\nrecords each successful op

Registry --> Calc : composition\n(introspects at construction)

History --> HistFile : write_to_file("history.txt")\nat all session exit points

note bottom of History
  Independent module — no dependency
  on Calculator or OperationRegistry.
  CLI mode does NOT use History.
end note

note bottom of CLI
  Does NOT use OperationHistory.
  Fail-fast: exits on first error.
end note

@enduml
